## 6. 📡 API Design

### Auth Routes (`/api/auth`)
| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/signup` | No | Register new user |
| POST | `/login` | No | Login |
| POST | `/refresh` | No | Refresh access token |
| POST | `/logout` | No | Clear cookies |
| GET | `/profile` | Yes | Get user profile + stats |

### URL Routes (`/api`)
| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/shorten` | Optional | Shorten a URL |
| GET | `/links` | Yes | Get user's links (paginated) |
| GET | `/links/:id` | Yes | Get single link |
| PUT | `/links/:id` | Yes | Update link |
| DELETE | `/links/:id` | Yes | Delete link |
| GET | `/links/:id/qr` | Yes | Get QR code (base64 PNG) |

### Analytics Routes (`/api/analytics`)
| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/:id` | Yes | Full analytics for a link |
| GET | `/:id/timeseries` | Yes | Time-series clicks |
| GET | `/dashboard` | Yes | Dashboard overview stats |

### Payment Routes (`/api/payments`)
| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/subscribe` | Yes | Create Razorpay subscription |
| POST | `/webhook` | No | Handle Razorpay webhook |
| GET | `/status` | Yes | Get subscription status |

### Redirect Route
```
GET /:shortCode  (regex: [a-zA-Z0-9_-]{3,30})
Defined AFTER all /api routes and page routes
```

